{"id":310384,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-湖北黄石市民胡芳家遭故意毁坏，报警110拒/","date":"2013-08-24T19:17:39Z","modified":"2013-08-24T19:17:39Z","title":"维权网 | 湖北黄石市民胡芳家遭故意毁坏，报警110拒接电话","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span> </span></p>\n<div><span> </span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员徐闯报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>24</span></span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>点左右，一群不明身份的人，其中十几个挂着长乐金融物流项目征收的胸牌，到湖北省黄石市下陆区新下陆庙宇垴村蒋家湾</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>45</span></span><span>号胡芳家，强行将家里人赶出家门，后用挖机将她们家夷为平地。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>据胡芳（手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>18772288446</span></span><span>）说：她们拨打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>110</span></span><span>报警，说：“一群人带着挖机毁坏我房子，请求救助”。但</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>110</span></span><span>听后直接挂掉电话，警察至现在（晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>51</span></span><span>分还没有任何警察到达现场）。胡芳说，从下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>55</span></span><span>分开始，她们每隔几分钟打一次电话，说一群人闯入她家，拆她们的房子，可</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>110</span></span><span>接通</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1-2</span></span><span>秒就挂了。同时她们向武汉公安厅投诉也没回电。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span> </span></span></span><span>据了解：从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>28</span></span><span>日起就不断的有不明身份的人到她的家中打砸，报警警察拒绝受理案件。经过多方投诉，直到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>22</span></span><span>日才拿到一份受理案件回执单，说是“正常拆迁”。针对她家各种家具被砸，人员没非法拘禁，没有任何说法。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </sp